N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 20.18 - Fluid cream product

State Regulations

Fluid cream product means cream (other than plastic cream
or frozen cream), including sterilized cream, or a mixture of cream and milk or
skim milk containing 9 percent or more butterfat, with or without the addition
of other ingredients. Notes
